Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.39,0:00:06.70,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.72,0:00:09.08,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.10,0:00:17.10,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.95,0:00:26.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.54,0:00:30.06,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.08,0:00:35.57,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.59,0:00:41.78,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.80,0:00:48.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.85,0:00:53.08,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.10,0:00:55.38,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.40,0:01:03.40,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.45,0:01:12.77,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.79,0:01:16.27,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.29,0:01:21.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.88,0:01:28.04,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, let's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.06,0:01:34.96,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.98,0:01:39.26,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.28,0:01:41.55,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.57,0:01:45.97,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.99,0:01:48.93,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.95,0:01:50.68,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.70,0:01:52.31,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.33,0:01:53.98,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.00,0:01:55.61,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:57.19,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.21,0:01:59.07,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.09,0:02:00.36,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.38,0:02:01.53,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:05.74,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.76,0:02:08.03,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.05,0:02:12.41,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.43,0:02:14.71,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.73,0:02:18.92,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.94,0:02:21.26,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.28,0:02:25.64,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:32.94,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.16,0:02:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.34,0:02:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.26,0:02:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything this \Nworld has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:03:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.55,0:03:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bounty hunters have left\Nto hunt the Straw Hat Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.51,0:03:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who have fallen for their trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.87,0:03:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A total bounty of 600 million Berries, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to see their Jolly Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.30,0:03:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we celebrate early?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.03,0:03:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May our beloved Papa, Don Accino,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Accino Family's knit\Nblood relations be blessed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.87,0:03:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here's to our present for Papa--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the heads of the Straw Hat Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.63,0:03:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Dream Sinking in the New World!\NThe Disillusioned Pirate, Puzzle"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.47,0:03:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The icebergs moved?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:03:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you morons?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.06,0:03:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:03:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural for icebergs to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water moves!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.03,0:04:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps that's not quite what they meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.17,0:04:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't moving because of the currents.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.22,0:04:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're moving of their own accord!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of their own accord?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't give us this crap\Nfirst thing in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch and see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun, if you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.08,0:04:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.83,0:04:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:05:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.35,0:05:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For chunks of ice, they're bossy punks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.28,0:05:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a mass of ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.62,0:05:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it definitely moved to block our path...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.18,0:05:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The iceberg itself seems normal enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were also those \NMarine ships last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.27,0:05:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like something is\Ntrying to lure us somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea who it is, \Nbut they've got guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:05:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's duke it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But first we have to figure out\Nwho exactly is behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.14,0:06:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vigaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vigaro...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vigaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.04,0:06:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vigaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle-san...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle-san is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.81,0:06:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.27,0:06:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.02,0:06:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a great physician!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.42,0:06:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not happy about getting called a\N"great physician" or anything, you punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jiro, what am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.94,0:07:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were attacked by some really\Nstrong guys in the New World...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.62,0:07:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are those guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put out the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.21,0:07:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drag your feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.11,0:07:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is an attack like that even possible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.72,0:07:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and carry the injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get us out of here as fast as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still weren't ready... for the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.99,0:07:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like Puzzle the \NPhoenix to sound defeated...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.06,0:07:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a whippersnapper \Nthat got in over my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.11,0:07:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, Puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've followed you because we believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.93,0:08:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.70,0:08:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.56,0:08:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle, I'll buy some time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stansen, bring out the raiding dory!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First Officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.49,0:08:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Vigaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.74,0:08:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't leave the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.62,0:08:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.36,0:08:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle, I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.12,0:08:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the man who will\Nbecome the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.67,0:08:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Vigaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.62,0:08:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, here it comes again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.72,0:08:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Meteors?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.14,0:08:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vigaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.81,0:09:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even First Officer Vigaro didn't last more\Nthan a few seconds up against them...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But during that brief period of time,\Nhe managed to destroy their rudder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to him, we were able to escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.62,0:09:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why everyone who\Nsurvived swore an oath!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.29,0:09:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should be like our first officer\Nand protect the captain with our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're absolutely right, Jiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.74,0:09:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be willing to lay down \Nmy life for Puzzle-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's protect the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.17,0:09:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.67,0:09:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then Stansen-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.51,0:09:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think Vigaro was willing\Nto sacrifice his life to protect yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.75,0:09:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare throw your life away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.38,0:10:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're working for a group \Nof bounty hunters...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that they're incredibly strong
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.94,0:10:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we were a mess after the New World...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand why we lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.26,0:10:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but then they stole our Jolly Roger...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.27,0:10:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our pride as the Phoenix Pirates....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.19,0:10:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.46,0:10:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stansen-san is a coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's all coming to an end today!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.34,0:10:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle the Phoenix has risen once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.63,0:10:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.26,0:10:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel fine now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gather the whole crew up on the deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.59,0:10:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The captain has regained consciousness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.57,0:10:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is that true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.05,0:10:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The day we've been\Ndying for has finally arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.98,0:10:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the revival of the Phoenix Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.10,0:11:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that damn Stansen will\Nget what's coming to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.02,0:11:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.52,0:11:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men, I'm sorry to have put you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.97,0:11:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.87,0:11:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imagining today made it easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle-san, I'm glad you're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.71,0:11:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.92,0:11:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.61,0:11:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.55,0:11:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.11,0:11:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.47,0:11:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only did what any doctor would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sure to pay you back someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time we meet will\Nbe in the New World, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.34,0:11:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were also headed for \Nthe New World, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.05,0:11:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that means we'll be\Nrivals from here on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:12:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can barely wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.21,0:12:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, we need to hop to \Nit and build up our forces
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.46,0:12:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we can return to the New World...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.39,0:12:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.93,0:12:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.73,0:12:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.43,0:12:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.24,0:12:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.90,0:12:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,aren't going back to the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.66,0:12:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stansen's decision was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.01,0:12:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to continue working\Nfor those bounty hunters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.18,0:12:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.21,0:12:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.68,0:12:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Have you lost your mind, Puzzle-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is willing to fight to\Nthe death, just like Vigaro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vigaro died... all for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.76,0:13:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle, I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.91,0:13:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the man who will\Nbecome the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.44,0:13:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we have you on our side, Puzzle-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been waiting this whole time\Nfor the Phoenix to rise from the ashes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Puzzle the Phoenix?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.58,0:13:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Phoenix...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,only existed\Nin the world of fairytales.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no right to go to the New World\Nwhen I couldn't protect my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you say that, Captain...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.63,0:13:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't accept that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our flag...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.18,0:13:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the Jolly Roger \Nthey stole from us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need a Jolly Roger anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:13:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.34,0:14:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you lost all sense of pride?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to thank you for tending to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.78,0:14:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm afraid we lost\Neverything in the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.69,0:14:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those waters...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.20,0:14:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World isn't as \Nforgiving as you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.98,0:14:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find out when I get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.23,0:14:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we're strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.52,0:14:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find out when I get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we're strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.96,0:14:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take the New World lightly, Puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.09,0:15:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Vigaro! I'm a phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.14,0:15:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.46,0:15:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.65,0:15:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's given up on their Jolly Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.91,0:15:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't pirates anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.08,0:15:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R... Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.94,0:15:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.90,0:16:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.51,0:16:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be fine without us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, take care of the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to swerve around to the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.17,0:16:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.45,0:16:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hard a-starboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.46,0:16:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hard a-starboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.26,0:16:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.03,0:16:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn us around!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.99,0:16:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The icebergs are gathering together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.55,0:16:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think you're taking us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.95,0:16:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.03,0:16:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rudder's not responding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.35,0:16:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the waterways got blocked,\Nit created those whirlpools.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:17:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is with these waters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.72,0:17:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna turn that into\Nshaved ice and gobble it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.51,0:17:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shaved ice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.62,0:17:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.10,0:17:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back in just a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.59,0:17:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.32,0:17:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a Devil Fruit power holder?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.29,0:17:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.50,0:17:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle Axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.85,0:17:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My shaved ice...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:17:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sunny is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.44,0:18:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Arctic Path.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.02,0:18:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any ship that wanders in never\Nsees the open ocean again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.46,0:18:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no mistaking him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.76,0:18:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Puzzle the Phoenix,\Nwith a bounty of 100 million Berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.22,0:18:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't he supposed to be dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been had!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.67,0:18:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Stansen guy tricked us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.83,0:18:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy,\Na 300-million-Berry bounty, is with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,bringing them to a total \Nof 400 million Berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.18,0:18:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is turning into something else!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.88,0:18:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry and inform Blend-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.59,0:18:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle the Phoenix is still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare the fallen pirates \Ndeceive the Accino Family?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've got some nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.52,0:18:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Siblings, we can add another present\Nto the list for our beloved Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.81,0:18:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to check on it right quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.39,0:18:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may handle things here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you take advantage of the \Nconfusion to grab onto Nami-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you using the paddle wheel?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.57,0:18:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky, where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.12,0:18:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was fully charging the cola\Nbarrels in the energy room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.58,0:19:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my guess is right, there will definitely\Ncome a time when we need them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.29,0:19:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, if we're ever going\Nto get out of these crazy waters...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.21,0:19:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...first we've got to unravel the\Npuzzle behind the moving icebergs!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.21,0:19:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be some sort of trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.28,0:19:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't mean squat to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.30,0:19:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be a cinch for us \Nto get out of this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.36,0:19:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.31,0:19:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dearies, now that you've\Nwandered into the Arctic Path,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll never get to see\Nthe open ocean ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say your prayers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to agree!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.61,0:19:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.62,0:19:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.53,0:20:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We always see eye-to-eye, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're stifling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.79,0:20:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That beautiful lady is \Nwith such a hideous man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.99,0:20:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.38,0:20:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I challenge you to a duel right here--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.68,0:20:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid we don't have \Ntime to play with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.39,0:20:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.78,0:20:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time we took our leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are dense!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were just telling you \Nthat there is no escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.59,0:20:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.40,0:20:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.14,0:20:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That expression was nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.93,0:20:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.91,0:20:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.26,0:20:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.55,0:20:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We always see eye-to-eye, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it, Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.88,0:20:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.24,0:20:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coup de...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:21:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.01,0:21:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What type of ship is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.48,0:21:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.96,0:21:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's really nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Salchow?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.38,0:21:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is f-flying away in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you expect me to believe that nonsense?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.70,0:21:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.14,0:21:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand that over!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.82,0:21:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, he's telling you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.11,0:21:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship is flying away\Nright before my very eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.78,0:21:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa, we've run into some trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.24,0:21:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not get the flag first?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.12,0:21:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a splendid idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.02,0:21:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said to get the flag first, my darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.48,0:21:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing, my honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.40,0:21:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lil-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:21:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you summon\Nthat one critter for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.67,0:21:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.35,0:21:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.26,0:21:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, um, I'm sorry, but you can't just--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.94,0:22:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lil-chan, you'd be doing it\Nas a favor for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.57,0:22:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus it was an order from our beloved Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.36,0:22:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, my kite, Uo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.30,0:22:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A strange fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.89,0:22:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At long last, we can finally relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.35,0:22:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ocean really is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.20,0:22:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue skies and white clouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.30,0:22:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shining sun and the flapping Jolly...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.18,0:22:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.77,0:22:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Jolly Roger is gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.05,0:23:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Zoro appears to be missing, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.25,0:23:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe they got lost again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.99,0:23:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.09,0:23:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brrr!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.00,0:23:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.41,0:23:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only are the icebergs \Ncold, but they keep moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.91,0:23:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet the others are taking it easy,\Ndrinking tea on the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.64,0:23:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that gaudy building?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.31,0:23:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Assassins Attack!\NThe Great Battle on Ice Begins"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.19,0:23:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
